{"tid":1463300,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇諗過我地一定唔可以輸既時候 對手呢鋪都一定唔可以輸","createTime":"2019-08-13T12:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:10:56.000Z","uid":125857,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f9ba912e5188a6295b0d292825bf5c54949ffc73","tid":1463300,"uid":125857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:40:24.000Z","msg":"我地今次唔可以輸 除左事後一定會大搜捕<br />\n智能燈柱 信用評級等等都會推出<br />\n但係我地既敵人都一樣 <span style=\"color: red;\">極權政府 濫權警隊 官商鄉黑</span> 如果我地贏左佢地一定會被清算<br />\n所以佢地每次行動都升級 濫捕濫告 射頭 毒打<br />\n每次都係殺人既心態上戰場<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>可唔可以唔好再對敵人咁仁慈 呢場係一場 唔係你死就係我亡既戰爭</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"7140486b7e2ddb9f295696e2ebc8343ef95dbdf1","tid":1463300,"uid":125857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:41:44.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"c67aac3fdb4692a53d0a9c96d41ecbe1d24613e1","tid":1463300,"uid":125857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:42:23.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母殺人政權"},{"pid":"e56e8ec237bd1c98da8ce86ffa390609963592bf","tid":1463300,"uid":125857,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:43:44.000Z","msg":"無數咁多受傷嘅手足 手機不盡嘅後遺症<br />\n邊個攬住敵人 打撚埋佢"},{"pid":"29acae39d1232e179e4138b43f7d5170d599307f","tid":1463300,"uid":125857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:44:23.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"1eba5b623c5f24c346375062e81f153115e5a525","tid":1463300,"uid":125857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:45:08.000Z","msg":"推你老母"},{"pid":"c2cefe69fcab0f3c459ae731b190f1da894d1178","tid":1463300,"uid":125857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:47:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5ca248040521735cb0c48a7bc7b953a2282ef2","tid":1463300,"uid":125857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:49